snippet.title: Victim Complex - Final Trailer
snippet.description:
The final trailer for Victim Complex, a first-person, narrative-driven horror experience. Wishlist now on Steam!

Victim Complex is releasing October 18, 2024. 

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2840800/Victim_Complex/

Trailer song: Knock Knock by Dmitry Taras. https://pixabay.com/music/build-up-scenes-knock-knock-horror-creepy-scary-thriller-trailer-teaser-177239/
